HEADWORD: Punkie
<hw>Punk"ie</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Orig. unknown.]</ety>
<def>A minute biting fly of the genus <gen>Ceratopogon</gen> or allied
genus of the family <fam>Chironomid⟦ae⟧</fam>, found in swarms in
various densely wooded or mountaneous regions.</def> <mark>[U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
